text: Victoriya Turks (born October 20, 1987) is a Ukrainian judoka. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the women's 78 kg event, in which she was eliminated in the second round by Anamari Velenšek. ==References== Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Ukrainian female judoka Category:Olympic judoka of Ukraine Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Universiade medalists in judo Category:Universiade gold medalists for Ukraine
